workout_items.name: Hollow Body Hold
workout_items.info:
INCREASE YOUR SETS +1 SO IF YOU'VE DONE 3, DO 4 THIS WEEK. 
------
60s hold

workout_items.name: Single Leg Kettlebell Romanian Deadlift
workout_items.info:
3 x 12 each side.

Do bodyweight if you dont have any weights

workout_items.name: Single Leg Hip Extension
workout_items.info:
3 x 15 each side.

Do bodyweight if you dont have any weights

workout_items.name: Band Pull Aparts
workout_items.info:
INCREASE YOUR SETS +1 SO IF YOU'VE DONE 3, DO 4 THIS WEEK. 
------

20 reps

workout_items.name: Bear Crawl Hold
workout_items.info: Hold position with feet just off ground for 60s

workout_items.name: Finisher
workout_items.info:
If you can pop outside;

200m Sprints then jog back x 10
or
3min skipping / 1 min rest x 3-6

inside;

30 air squats
12 press ups
x4
